            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Generate Class Sessions?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-6">Confirm the generation of class sessions for this module. Would you also like to sync them with Google Calendar?</p>
            <div class="flex justify-end gap-3">
                <button class="px-4 py-2 border border-input rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors focus:outline-none" @onclick="CancelGenerateSessionsConfirm">Cancel</button>
                <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-secondary text-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80 border border-border rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus:outline-none" @onclick="ConfirmGenerateSessionsOnly">Generate Sessions</button>
                <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus:outline-none" @onclick="ConfirmGenerateSessionsAndSync">Sync with Google Calendar</button>
